metadata.description: Pasithea Therapeutics Corp., a biotechnology company, engages in research and discovery of treatments for psychiatric and neurological disorders. The company also intends to operate anti-depression clinics and provide business support services using trained pharmacists to administer intravenous infusions of ketamine. Pasithea Therapeutics Corp. was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Miami Beach, Florida.
